work for the blind

1205
01:13:37,246 --> 01:13:41,114
No, you must study, you've
to go to USA

1206
01:13:42,684 --> 01:13:44,743
Don't worry about me

1207
01:13:45,721 --> 01:13:46,346
Wo

1208
01:13:46,688 --> 01:13:51,523
If you go abroad, you'll set
an example for the blind in HK

1209
01:13:51,693 --> 01:13:53,524
