1212
01:14:01,870 --> 01:14:03,861
If you accept this scholarship,

1213
01:14:04,039 --> 01:14:07,975
may be they'll grant another
scholarship to other Chinese

1214
01:14:08,210 --> 01:14:12,374
After your graduates, you can
teach the other blind people,

1215
01:14:12,548 --> 01:14:15,676
so they don't have to rely
on foreign help alone

