1230
01:14:59,928 --> 01:15:01,725
Alright, I will speak slowly...

1231
01:15:02,664 --> 01:15:05,599
No, you must learn now
we don't have much time

1232
01:15:05,934 --> 01:15:08,732
I won't be with you for very long

1233
01:15:20,782 --> 01:15:21,771
Wo

